1
00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:07,410
A terrified cat has survived a 5 mi round trip under the engine cover of a car on a school run

2
00:00:08,030 --> 00:00:19,420
The black cat was found curled up under the engine cover of David King's car when he decided to do an oil check after dropping his grandson off at school in Kent

3
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:27,100
Mr King's wife said her husband had come running in and was shouting for me to come have a look

4
00:00:27,330 --> 00:00:29,660
We weren't even sure it was alive

5
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:36,800
so I gently pushed it with a stick to check it was breathing and saw it was a terrified little cat

6
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:41,110
It reversed even further into the engine and was stuck

7
00:00:41,490 --> 00:00:42,850
I tried to reach it

8
00:00:42,860 --> 00:00:46,730
but it was too far down and there wasn't any way I could get it out

9
00:00:46,990 --> 00:00:53,050
Any way I could get it out Following a rescue by UK charity Cat's Protection

10
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:56,860
the four year old cat was later reunited with its owner

